Beside the camp entrance ahead, ZOLAYA stands with her back turned, PETTING A HORSE streaked with DIRT AND BLOOD.
LORATH stands watch. Itâ€™s a comforting sight.

LORATH whirls. 
ZOLAYA TURNS, stunned to see OYUUN limping toward her.
Oyuun and Zolaya rush together and collide in an EMBRACE--two halves, made whole. You join Lorath, giving them space.
They part slightly to face each other. Close and intimate.
They renew the embrace, squeezing tightly.

Oyuun notices Lorath. Zolaya senses her question.
Nods to player at "this one"
Zolaya PREPS THE HORSE and then MOUNTS IT as Oyuun speaks
Zolaya PULLS OYUUN UP behind her onto the horse.
Zolaya takes the reins, ready to go.
Oyuun and Zolaya RIDE AWAY. Lorath watches them go.
